1
00:00:48,730 --> 00:00:49,730
Senior brother,

2
00:00:50,160 --> 00:00:51,220
I am feeling unwell

3
00:00:51,430 --> 00:00:52,700
and wish to see the Director.

4
00:00:52,700 --> 00:00:53,660
The Director is resting.

5
00:00:53,660 --> 00:00:55,330
What is it, Vice Director Shen?

6
00:00:55,330 --> 00:00:56,590
I dreamed of my father.

7
00:00:56,660 --> 00:00:59,100
He said the great cause of the Dragon Vein is still missing a piece,

8
00:00:59,100 --> 00:00:59,700
and asked me

9
00:00:59,700 --> 00:01:00,630
to offer my help.

10
00:01:01,000 --> 00:01:01,800
Wait a moment, Vice Director Shen.

11
00:01:01,800 --> 00:01:02,730
I will go report.

12
00:01:06,030 --> 00:01:06,900
The Director invites you

13
00:01:06,900 --> 00:01:08,300
to meet at the alchemy room on the second floor.

14
00:01:08,300 --> 00:01:08,930
Thank you.

15
00:01:13,630 --> 00:01:14,490
Please come in.

16
00:01:17,000 --> 00:01:19,000
Vice Director Shen, visiting so late at night.

17
00:01:19,000 --> 00:01:20,400
Did you have an epiphany?

18
00:01:20,900 --> 00:01:22,330
My father came to me in a dream,

19
00:01:22,330 --> 00:01:23,360
leaving me uneasy.

20
00:01:23,360 --> 00:01:25,030
I came specifically to seek your guidance, Director.

21
00:01:25,030 --> 00:01:27,630
I wish to do my meager part for the great cause.

22
00:01:29,460 --> 00:01:31,130
This is the essence of the Soul-Locking Pill.

23
00:01:31,130 --> 00:01:33,530
Once refined, it helps stabilize the soul.

24
00:01:34,130 --> 00:01:35,530
These talisman fragments are

25
00:01:35,530 --> 00:01:37,729
Soul-Calming Talismans drawn by the monks of Ci'en Temple.

26
00:01:37,729 --> 00:01:39,860
Blending them into the pill will increase its efficacy.

27
00:01:39,860 --> 00:01:40,600
Ci'en Temple.

28
00:01:40,600 --> 00:01:41,600
The carved letters on the oil lamp.

29
00:01:41,600 --> 00:01:42,700
The source of the talismans.

30
00:01:42,700 --> 00:01:44,700
They are indeed closely connected.

31
00:01:48,200 --> 00:01:48,960
Datura.

32
00:01:49,000 --> 00:01:49,830
Bloodstone.

33
00:01:50,000 --> 00:01:52,130
To condense and consolidate the soul.

34
00:01:53,560 --> 00:01:54,130
Useless!

35
00:01:54,460 --> 00:01:55,930
Another ruined batch.

36
00:02:08,500 --> 00:02:10,030
The soul power is unstable.

37
00:02:10,100 --> 00:02:11,060
The implanted soul seed

38
00:02:11,060 --> 00:02:12,730
is showing signs of rejection.

39
00:02:12,730 --> 00:02:13,460
Drag him away

40
00:02:14,200 --> 00:02:16,329
and feed him to the Dragon Marrow Pool.

41
00:02:18,329 --> 00:02:19,990
Bullshit Soul-Locking Pill!

42
00:02:20,030 --> 00:02:21,700
It's clearly a Soul-Devouring Pill.

43
00:02:21,700 --> 00:02:23,360
Take too many, and you'll become like us,

44
00:02:23,360 --> 00:02:24,430
the walking dead!

45
00:02:26,960 --> 00:02:28,400
7:45 PM.

46
00:02:28,800 --> 00:02:30,530
The west side door.

47
00:02:33,329 --> 00:02:34,230
Director.

48
00:02:35,100 --> 00:02:35,800
Why did this person

49
00:02:35,800 --> 00:02:37,800
suddenly go mad and spout nonsense?

50
00:02:39,329 --> 00:02:41,600
I will investigate this thoroughly.

51
00:02:42,030 --> 00:02:43,260
You must be startled, Vice Director Shen.

52
00:02:43,260 --> 00:02:44,829
Go back to your room and rest.

53
00:02:44,829 --> 00:02:45,500
Director.

54
00:02:53,700 --> 00:02:54,800
Don't touch Secretary Shen!

55
00:02:54,800 --> 00:02:55,460
His Highness ordered me

56
00:02:55,460 --> 00:02:56,990
to wait here for a long time.

57
00:02:57,530 --> 00:03:00,160
His Highness already knows the Director is an imposter.

58
00:03:00,160 --> 00:03:01,930
Lord Shen is suspected to be imprisoned at the bottom of the tower.

59
00:03:01,930 --> 00:03:04,260
But only the Director knows the entrance.

60
00:03:16,900 --> 00:03:17,960
Hand over Shen Mo,

61
00:03:18,460 --> 00:03:19,700
and I will spare your life.

62
00:03:19,700 --> 00:03:21,400
The Crown Prince's appointment...

63
00:03:21,400 --> 00:03:22,800
How did an outsider know?

64
00:03:24,660 --> 00:03:27,300
There's a mole. Let's fight our way out first!

65
00:03:33,800 --> 00:03:35,000
Who sent you?

66
00:03:35,329 --> 00:03:37,930
The Imperial City Department or the Director?

67
00:03:39,829 --> 00:03:41,230
Medicine mixed in blood.

68
00:03:44,700 --> 00:03:45,500
They are medicine men.

69
00:03:45,500 --> 00:03:46,900
Qin Muzhi's death squad.

70
00:03:47,230 --> 00:03:47,900
Soaked in drugs.

71
00:03:47,900 --> 00:03:49,760
They've lost their sense of pain.

72
00:03:56,160 --> 00:03:58,300
His Highness asked me to pass on a message.

73
00:03:58,300 --> 00:03:59,500
The Director is the Earth Immortal Old Man.

74
00:03:59,500 --> 00:04:01,300
The old monster who should have died 30 years ago.

75
00:04:01,300 --> 00:04:02,860
Since the Crown Prince knows,

76
00:04:02,860 --> 00:04:04,520
why not report to His Majesty?

77
00:04:07,260 --> 00:04:09,460
Our informants only heard from the bottom of the passage

78
00:04:09,460 --> 00:04:11,520
that there was occasional coughing.

79
00:04:11,530 --> 00:04:13,590
They couldn't see it for themselves.

80
00:04:13,930 --> 00:04:15,760
His Highness intercepted fragments of a secret letter.

81
00:04:15,760 --> 00:04:17,329
They are preparing a blood sacrifice,

82
00:04:17,329 --> 00:04:19,899
requiring seven people with special birth dates,

83
00:04:19,899 --> 00:04:21,959
and using pure Yang blood as a primer.

84
00:04:22,930 --> 00:04:25,360
The Imperial Astronomical Bureau will hold a ritual at Ci'en Temple.

85
00:04:25,360 --> 00:04:26,560
Is it related to this?

86
00:04:28,060 --> 00:04:29,300
The ritual is just a front,

87
00:04:29,300 --> 00:04:31,760
actually used to screen and mark believers.

88
00:04:32,700 --> 00:04:35,300
They plant soul seeds as a source of soul power.

89
00:04:42,130 --> 00:04:43,230
The medicine men are sustained by drugs.

90
00:04:43,230 --> 00:04:45,290
There must be a core gathering point.

91
00:04:45,760 --> 00:04:47,530
He could still move despite the severe injury to his left arm,

92
00:04:47,530 --> 00:04:50,260
but his right arm kept protecting his left chest.

93
00:04:54,600 --> 00:04:58,260
The medicine core and the blood pool liquid share the same origin.

94
00:05:02,460 --> 00:05:04,900
The communication bugs come in a male and female pair.

95
00:05:04,900 --> 00:05:06,300
His Highness has the female bug.

96
00:05:06,300 --> 00:05:08,000
It can be sensed within ten miles

97
00:05:08,000 --> 00:05:09,160
and used for communication.
